Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.27,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.98,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:13.15,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:18.28,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:31.05,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:39.47,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:51.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:02.29,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:07.75,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:17.05,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:28.65,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(372,326,339,326,0,3989)}Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:29.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, Ryuzaki says he wants\Nyou to help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested,\Ncome immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to find a way to get\Ninvolved in the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought L himself\Nwould ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can get inside information\Nabout the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and about the fake Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find out about Fake Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before anyone else at\Ntask force headquarters does...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:58.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, we both want to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Ryuzaki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Asahi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, would it be all right if\NI'm Light Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do. I will call you Light here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at our current information\Non Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want you to examine this video,\Nwhich was sent to the television station...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but was never released to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking any material from this room\Nor taking notes is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:35.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.39,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,460)\fad(209,0)}The Previous Night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to hide the possibility that\Nthere is a second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and ask Light Yagami\Nto investigate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But wouldn't that make it difficult\Nfor Light to help with the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Why do you want him\Nto work with us anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only going\Nto hide that from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:06.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until we have him watch this tape\Nand ask him for his impression of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something amazing\Nabout Light's deductive skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he sees this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he may even deduce that\Nthere is a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only basis for\Na second Kira is your explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the victims of those killings\Nhad committed minor crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that never would have been\Npunished by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:33.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira that we've presumed until now\Nneeded a face and a name to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But judging from the fact that\NMr. Ukita was killed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as he arrived at\Nthe television station,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and considering how Kira practically\Ntold me that he could kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if I just appeared on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,means that the Second Kira can kill\Nby just seeing someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:54.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll ask Light to look\Nat the investigative facts and the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he suggests that there may\Nbe a second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then he's almost completely cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's Kira, he'll want to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the one in charge of\Nthe investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:13.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, if I go along with\Nthe Second Kira's demands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and appear three days later on TV,\NI will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that Kira would miss\Nan easy chance to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what you're saying is that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if my son doesn't deduce that\Nthere is a second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then you'll continue to suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:31.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. In that case, it will remain below\Na five-percent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll tell him that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we are investigating the possibility of\Na second Kira and have him assist us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:46.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing that, I trust\Nyou now believe that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Could it be that the reason...\N- On the given day and time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why I feel so disgusted\Nwhen I watch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is because I'm the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than just\Nabout tarnishing Kira 's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So why isn't-?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone giving me any explanation\Nabout this video?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything careless\Nabout this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave the situation alone,\NL will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:17.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what do you think?\NDid you get something from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be more than one person\Nwho has Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's power?!\NLight, what do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a good chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this is not the Kira\Nwe've known up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now, Kira's never used suspects\Nlike these for his announced killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Kira needs a face\Nand a name to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it strange that he was able\Nto kill the detective and officers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who happened to rush\Nto the television-station building?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly the same deduction as L,\NI mean Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good job, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be cleared now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think we are looking\Nat a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:07.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew, Ryuga,\NI mean Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you test me, knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not convincing if I'm the only one\Nwho argues that there is a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With you coming to\Nthe same conclusion as I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my theory becomes more believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been of great assistance to me,\NLight. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We first have to stop the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He obviously sympathizes with Kira,\Nand is not very bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'll obey the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we make a fake message\Nfrom the real Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a good chance that\Nwe can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected of you, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought that would\Nbe the best idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to play\Nthe part of the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. With your genius,\Nyou should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we don't have\Nany time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you script a message\Nfrom Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to air on tonight's news?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He planned from the beginning\Nto bring me here to play this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've portrayed\NKira convincingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is very good,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,though if we don't remove\Nthe part which says, "You're free to kill L,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when pretending to be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:46.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he would demand\Nthat you be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a bit of a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change that to\Nwhatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aihara, the script is ready.\NI leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now a shocking development.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In response to the video that was sent\Nand aired on Sakura TV a few days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,another person claiming to be\Nthe real Kira has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:14.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has ordered several\Ntelevision stations to air his message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police department has\Nauthorized us to broadcast this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the real Kira?\NIs this another Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, please take a look at the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira responded!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the true Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:40.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira who was shown\Non Sakura TV is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being lenient to the impostor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:51.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I know he was\Nonly trying to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:56.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But killing the innocent is\Nagainst my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:03.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the impostor truly sympathizes\Nwith me and wants to help my cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:08.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask that he refrain from killing aimlessly,\Nand accept my basic principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- If you ignore this warning...\N- All right! The video, the video!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- and continue to be reckless...\N- What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to reply to him,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.54,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,460)}Several days later
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,397)}Ryuzaki! It's a reply from\Nthe Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N- It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring the entire envelope there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall play a copy on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kira, thank you for your reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:47.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l will do as you say," huh?\NI don't know if I can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really knows Kira's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:54.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he would force L to appear\Non TV and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall for something like this...\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have the eyes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He talked about the Shinigami eyes\Non a tape the whole world will see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just said that he didn't\Nhave "the eyes," didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:18.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows-?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me how I can meet you\Nwithout the police finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we can confirm our identities\Nby showing our Shinigami to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something fast\Nabout this guy, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:35.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shini...gami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:53.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to accept the existence\Nof something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:12.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we supposed to accept\Nthe existence of something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Ryuzaki.\NShinigami don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:30.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira had those criminals in prison\Nwrite something about Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:35.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So shouldn't we assume that\Nthis is the same Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same person,\Nso they say the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:45.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the same Kira from before,\Nhe wouldn't have replied to our video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that the real Kira\Nwould go through the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:53.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of getting L to appear on TV,\Nonly to stop trying to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe the real Kira and\Nthe Second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,already have established\Na connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And decided to use the word "Shinigami"\Nto throw off the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Light says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the two Kiras were connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that he would stop\Ntrying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:17.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Kira is acting independent\Nof the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to meet the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:25.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NHe's acting out of interest in Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinigami" probably refers to\Ntheir killing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can confirm our identities by showing\Nour Shinigami to each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,probably means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can confirm our identities by\Nshowing each other our killing power."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "Shinigami" is\Na word that has
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:50.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,some meaning between\NKira and Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:55.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should try to get him to\Ntell us what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to respond\Nand force him to be more direct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:04.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't ask him properly,\Nhe'll know that we're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:09.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I shall leave the rest to\NKira and Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:18.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Kira has received\Na message from Kira and is satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks that he's got Kira's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he also used a word that\Nonly the two of them would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This reply will air today on\NSakura TV's six o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Kira should be watching\Nthe exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,between our made-up Kira\Nand the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From Kira's viewpoint, he'll want\Nto prevent the Second Kira from coming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,into direct contact with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:51.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this time, the real Kira\Nwill feel pressured to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Kira doesn't-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:01.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I thought of what we could do\Nwith the Second Kira in that case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:06.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he reveals more information\Nthat Kira doesn't want the police to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and makes Kira more nervous and furious,\Nin order to pressure Kira into meeting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be more interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if Kira gets scared and sends a reply\Nin order to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:23.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance we'll obtain some\Nphysical evidence from Kira himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's focus on gathering all the information\Nwe can from the Second Kira's package.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, just great, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Modeling sure uses a lot of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami always have to have\Na Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So to give one to a human\Nto play with,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Shinigami needs to have\Ntwo Death Notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that Ryuk,\Nwho gave the extra Death Note to Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was able to trick the Shinigami King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:18.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The Shinigami King isn't\Neasy to fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:25.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just say... I'm one of the few\Nin the Shinigami Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:31.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who know how to kill a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:37.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then you killed a Shinigami\Nand gave his notebook to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:45.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be around\Nwhen a Shinigami died...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell me how to kill a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to kill a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is to make them fall\Nin love with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful way to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There once was a Shinigami\Nnamed Gelus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:21.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who used to watch a certain girl\Nfrom the Shinigami Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelus was always looking\Nat that girl from the Shinigami Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's today, isn't it?\NThe end of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so healthy.\NI wonder why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:49.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know how she\Nwas going to die too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and decided to watch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was walking alone\Nat night on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly from an alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:20.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a man appeared and confessed\Nhis love for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more\Nthan anyone else in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching you!\NI want to protect you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a man she didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl turned him down, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then kill myself-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelus did something that\Na Shinigami should never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelus used his Death Note\Nto save the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:28.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami shorten human lives.\NThey only exist to take lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:51.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Gelus became something\Nwhich was neither sand nor rust, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only his Death Note was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:08.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Gelus' remaining life was transferred\Nto the girl whose life he saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that the Shinigami\Nwouldn't have died
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if he hadn't fallen in love\Nwith that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:28.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a Shinigami named Gelus\Nwho saved me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:29.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gelus was in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:37.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that notebook is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:39.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In order to kill a Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you need him to fall in love with\Na human and save that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Rem?\NAre you in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:58.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:06.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have something\NI can tell Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:12.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he knows?\NHow to kill a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:18.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him on TV,\N"Please tell me how I can meet you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he hasn't replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go and tell him\Nsomething again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave the Second Kira\Nalone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:37.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Second Kira makes a fatal slip-up\Nand is caught by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a chance that the police\Nwill find out about the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:43.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A strawberry sundae please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I contact the Second Kira\Nwithout L noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet Kira soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But at any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a person are you,\NFake Kira-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a person are you, Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:28.22,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.56,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:42.61,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:48.99,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.58,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.25,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:06.72,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:11.89,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:22.65,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:28.49,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:37.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May 22nd, my friend and I showed off\Nour notebooks in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:42.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Fake Kira is caught,\NI'll have to get my hands on his notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:45.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case scenario,\NI may have to kill everyone there.
